    "The Zope Web Application Construction Kit":http://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/tg/detail/-/0672321335/qid=1030511472/sr=1-5/ref=sr_1_5/002-3988880-4512056?v=glance&amp;s=books edited by Martina Brockman, et. al.

