  Mailing Lists

    "Zope.org":http://www.zope.org/Resources/MailingLists maintains a
    collection of the many Zope mailing lists.

  Python Information

    "Python.org":http://www.python.org has lots of information about
    Python including a tutorial and reference documentation.
